<article articleID="LBsn_00018_F001">
<quotation>
<citation>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「僕が逮捕されたときには『三谷容疑者』とやさしく呼んでくださ<sampling type="start" />い」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</citation>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　メガネベストドレッサー賞授賞式にて</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<citation>
<source>
<sentence type="quasi">（出典・年月不明）</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</source>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「お母さん、近眼に産んでくれてありがとう！」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</citation>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　今のライバルは？</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">の質問に</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<citation>
<source>
<sentence type="quasi">（出典・年月不明）</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</source>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「昔はカール・ルイスと答えるようにしてたんですが…同い年なんですよ、カールとは。</sentence>
<sentence>関係ないですが、ダイアナさんも同い年です。</sentence>
<sentence>でも、ここんとこのライバルは、やはり安室奈美恵ですかね。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">いまに見ていろって感じです」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</citation>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　ヤクルト対巨人戦の副音声で、松井選手の背番号５５の由来について</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<citation>
<source>
<sentence type="quasi">（ヤクルトＶＳ巨人戦の副音声の放送にて、年月不明）</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</source>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「コント５５号？」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</citation>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　ジャングルＴＶで</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<citation>
<source>
<sentence type="quasi">（年月不明）</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</source>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">関根勤</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「奥さんはどんな料理をつくられるんですか？」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">三谷</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「そうですねぇ…キャベツの姿煮とか…」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
</citation>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　<quote>「みんなのいえ」</quote>試写会舞台挨拶の際、自ら上映前の注意をされて</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<citation>
<source>
<sentence type="quasi">（年月不明）</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</source>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「携帯電話、ＰＨＳをお持ちの方は電源をお切りください。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">ポケットベルをお持ちの方は…そろそろ携帯にしたほうがいいですよ」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</citation>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　ヤクルト対巨人戦副音声より</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<citation>
<source>
<sentence type="quasi">（００年７月）</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</source>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">三谷</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「このピッチャーの方（巨人　西山投手）はなぜこうやって顔を（グローブで）隠すんですか？」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">関根潤三</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「クセです。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">（略）それとしょっちゅう口半開きにしてますから、それ隠すのもあるかもしれません」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">三谷</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「よく口臭のある方はこうやって隠しながらしゃべりますよね」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">荒瀬詩織アナ</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「そうじゃないと思います」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
</citation>
</quotation>
<titleBlock>
<title>
<sentence type="quasi">興味</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</title>
</titleBlock>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　<quote>「今夜、宇宙の片隅で」</quote>制作発表にて</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<citation>
<source>
<sentence type="quasi">（９８年６月）</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</source>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「僕は西村（雅彦）とは（つきあいが）長いんですけれども、ま、確かに役者としては非常に信頼をおいていますが、人間としては僕は石橋（貴明）さんのほうが好きです。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">肉体的には飯島（直子）さんのほうに関心があります」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</citation>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　シアタートップス、カワサキさんの質問</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<citation>
<source>
<sentence type="quasi">（出典・年月不明）</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</source>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">私</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「お好きな食べ物はなんですか？」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">三谷</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「はぁ…たたみイワシとか」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">私</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「たたみイワシ以外では？」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">三谷</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「イワシ関係ならなんでも」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">私</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「お好きな色は？」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">三谷</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「人生ゲームではいつも緑のコマを」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
</citation>
</quotation>
<titleBlock>
<title>
<sentence type="quasi">愛</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</title>
</titleBlock>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　テレパル</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<citation>
<source>
<sentence type="quasi">（９８年７月）</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</source>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「結婚生活、二人でいるときはいまの自分の気持ちを託して即興で歌ったりします。</sentence>
<sentence>どんな歌かはここでは歌えません。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">でもみんなやってることでしょう」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</citation>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　小林聡美との入籍会見の際</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<citation>
<source>
<sentence type="quasi">（出典不明）</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</source>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「友達が遊びにこないような家庭にしたいね」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</citation>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><quote><sentence>　「笑っていいとも！</sentence>
」</quote>より</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<citation>
<source>
<sentence type="quasi">（年月不明）</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</source>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">三谷</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「僕がテレビに出ると妻がとてもいやがるんです」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">タモリ</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「なんで」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">三谷</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「独占したいんじゃ…」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
</citation>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　小林聡美との入籍会見で―なぜ入籍を？</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">の質問に</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<citation>
<source>
<sentence type="quasi">（出典不明）</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</source>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「マンションを買うのに名義が違うと富士銀行がお金を貸してくれなかったので」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</citation>
</quotation>
<titleBlock>
<title>
<sentence type="quasi">友情</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</title>
</titleBlock>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　テレビライフの９６年脚本賞の授賞式で</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<citation>
<source>
<sentence type="quasi">（出典不明）</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</source>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「西村もそうですけど、いまがピークだと思うんで、彼と僕とで、どっちが先に仕事がなくなるか、僕は彼だと思います」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</citation>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　<quote>「めざましテレビ」</quote>電<sampling type="end" />話出演より</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</article>
</sample>
